   - If H is the text "N/A" (case‑insensitive), write "N/A".
   - Else if H is empty/None, write "No".
   - Else if H is a number (Excel stores dates as numbers) or the text "Yes" (case‑insensitive), write "Yes".
   - Otherwise write "No".
